'''鄺健雄牧師'''（'''Lawrence Khong'''，{{bd|1952年||}}）是[[新加坡|新加坡]]{{link-en|堅信浸信會|Faith_Community_Baptist_Church}}的主任牧師，堅信浸信會是新加坡的一間大型教會，會友約九千人<ref name=abtfcbf>[http://www.fcbc.org.sg/pdf/AboutFCBC_Eng007.pdf "About FCBC"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927180042/http://www.fcbc.org.sg/pdf/AboutFCBC_Eng007.pdf |date=2011-09-27 }}, Retrieved 5 October 2009</ref><ref name=fcbcwebsite>{{cite web |url=http://www.fcbc.org.sg/index.asp |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-11-05  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100405082102/http://www.fcbc.org.sg/index.asp |archivedate=2010-04-05 }}</ref>。

==生平==
鄺健雄在2000年被國際使徒聯盟（International Coalition of Apostles）的{{link-en|彼得·魏格納|C._Peter_Wagner}}牧師按立為[[使徒|使徒]]。鄺健雄是触爱社会服务的創辦人及負責人，触爱社会服务是一個新加坡的非營利性組織，在新加坡有十八個據點。<ref name=tcs>[http://www.tcs.org.sg/corp_info/lk_profile.php "TOUCH Community Services Corporate Information"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tcs.org.sg/corp_info/lk_profile.php |date=20190614064200 }}, Retrieved 5 Oct 2009</ref>。

鄺健雄在堅信浸信會中強調[[細胞小組|小組]]的功能．並提出「[[小組教會|小組教會]]」的概念，有著書《使徒性小組教會: 從堅信浸信教會看增長與佈道的實用策略》。

鄺健雄除了是堅信浸信會的主任牧師外，也是專業的[[魔術師|魔術師]]<ref>[http://news.dhf.org.tw/News.aspx?cate=11&key=3714 是牧師也是魔術師　鄺健雄：順服呼召進入演藝圈！]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，曾以魔術劇的形式在教會[[佈道|佈道]]。近年來領受神的呼召，開始製作電影，進入媒體及演藝圈<ref name=today>[http://www.fcbc.org.sg/fcbc_mediacenter_019.asp "Destiny with HD"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601235730/http://www.fcbc.org.sg/fcbc_mediacenter_019.asp |date=2010-06-01 }}, TODAY, 25 September 2003</ref><ref name=stdramas>[http://www.fcbc.org.sg/fcbc_mediacenter_021.asp "Digital dramas"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527091648/http://www.fcbc.org.sg/fcbc_mediacenter_021.asp |date=2009-05-27 }}, The Straits Times, 14 October 2003</ref>，製作魔術劇《神奇的愛》（Magic of Love）和《幻影情真》（Magic Box），作為和非基督徒傳福音的管道<ref name = bkref1>Lawrence Khong (2008) ''Give me the Multitudes! Obeying God's Call into the Media World'', TOUCH Ministries International: Singapore</ref><ref name="zhchris">{{Cite web |url=http://chinese.christianpost.com/article/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4-%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E6%B3%95-%E5%B0%87%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD-13821/ |title=新加坡牧師警告：廢除「同性戀法」將威脅到家庭 |access-date=2013-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126082350/http://chinese.christianpost.com/article/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4-%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E6%B3%95-%E5%B0%87%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD-13821/ |archive-date=2013-01-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

鄺健雄公開對[[LGBT|同性戀、雙性戀、跨性別（LGBT）]]議題表達強烈反對，引發新加坡公眾對他的非議；他堅決反對廢除將同性間性行為視為違法的《[[新加坡刑法|新加坡刑法]]》第377A條，並多次表示要捍衛「家庭」（Family）和「基本構建」（basic building block）。<ref name="zhchris"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mothership.sg/2015/06/pastor-lawrence-khong-we-will-wear-white-until-the-pink-is-gone/ |title=Pastor Lawrence Khong: ‘We will wear white until the pink is gone’ |access-date=2016-09-30 |archive-date=2016-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616161739/http://mothership.sg/2015/06/pastor-lawrence-khong-we-will-wear-white-until-the-pink-is-gone/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/ikea-singapore-reviewing-support-for-pastors-magic-show-after-backlash-from-gay-rights |title=Ikea Singapore reviewing support for pastor's magic show after backlash from gay rights groups |access-date=2016-09-30 |archive-date=2018-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622165330/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/ikea-singapore-reviewing-support-for-pastors-magic-show-after-backlash-from-gay-rights |dead-url=no }}</ref>鄺健雄近年來呼籲基督徒信眾支持原本由回教徒發起的「穿白衣運動」，以抗議年度聲援LGBT的集會[[Pink_Dot_SG|Pink Dot SG]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.zaobao.com.sg/special/outline/story20140629-360310 |title=“粉红色”聚会人数剧增 “穿白”运动相对受冷落 |access-date=2016-09-30 |archive-date=2016-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002160045/http://www.zaobao.com.sg/special/outline/story20140629-360310 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theonlinecitizen.com/2015/06/15/lawrence-khong-pink-dot-vandalises-singapore-with-their-propaganda/ |title=Lawrence Khong: “Pink Dot ‘vandalises’ Singapore with their propaganda |access-date=2016-09-30 |archive-date=2017-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104234927/https://www.theonlinecitizen.com/2015/06/15/lawrence-khong-pink-dot-vandalises-singapore-with-their-propaganda/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

